Merge all splice variants of an expression dataset into unique locus, unaware of alternative splicing, by summing all variants for the same gene

Source: R/fct_normalisation.R
aggregate_splice_variants.Rd

Merge all splice variants of an expression dataset into unique locus, unaware of alternative splicing, by summing all variants for the same gene

aggregate_splice_variants(data)

Arguments

data

dataframe : expression data with splice variants as rownames

Value

dataframe with agregated rows

Examples

data("abiotic_stresses")
aggregate_splice_variants(abiotic_stresses$normalized_counts)
